                    <p><strong>Choose the correct tense by clicking on your choice:</strong></p>
                    <div class="multiple-choice">
                        1. Maria <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'discovered')" data-question="5_1">discovered</span> / <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'has discovered')" data-question="5_1">has discovered</span> postcrossing last year.
                    </div>
                    <div class="multiple-choice">
                        2. She <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'sent')" data-question="5_2">sent</span> / <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'has sent')" data-question="5_2">has sent</span> her first postcard to Japan.
                    </div>
                    <div class="multiple-choice">
                        3. Since then, she <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'received')" data-question="5_3">received</span> / <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'has received')" data-question="5_3">has received</span> many postcards.
                    </div>
                    <div class="multiple-choice">
                        4. Last month, Maria <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'got')" data-question="5_4">got</span> / <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'has got')" data-question="5_4">has got</span> a postcard from Nepal.
                    </div>
                    <div class="multiple-choice">
                        5. She <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'never heard')" data-question="5_5">never heard</span> / <span class="choice-button" onclick="selectChoice(this, 'has never heard')" data-question="5_5">has never heard</span> of Tasmania before postcrossing.
                    </div>
                    <div class="score-display" id="score5"></div>
